-- Criminal probe focuses on JPMorgan employees in London: source
-- 
-- Fri Jul 13, 2012 1:46pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/13/us-jpmorgan-probe-idUSBRE86C0YD20120713

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - A criminal investigation into employees of JPMorgan Chase & Co is focusing on several people who worked for JPMorgan in London, a source said. 
 JPMorgan said earlier on Friday that some of its traders may have concealed losses in a derivatives book. (Reporting By  Matthew Goldstein , writing by Dan Wilchins; Editing by Gerald E. McCormick)